  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="6191261">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/6191261/" class="title-link">古代蒙学教育流程的经典设计</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-6191261"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/46026707/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u46026707-10.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/46026707/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">子不雨</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2013-07-31"
      class="main-meta">2013-07-31 17:27:18</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_6191261_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  《三字经》是一本由宋代人编纂的儿童启蒙读物。要是在古代，我们入学第一课学的就不是语文的a o e、数学的1 2 3了，而是人手一本《三字经》，读着朗朗上口的“人之初，性本善”。  《三字经》作为古代蒙学教育的起点教材，据说已经通行了700多年。我是等我长到20多岁才系统地、...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/6191261/#comments">(2回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">9有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_6191261_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_6191261_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="2993194">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/2993194/" class="title-link">我的小感想</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-2993194"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/codezjl1103/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u4602026-77.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/codezjl1103/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">轻舟</span>
